    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean even if it cuts a utility bill, that's a long shot compared to the huge upfront cost of new gear. feels like the people making these rules dont really get the math for a local business. do you think these regulations are actually based on sound economic reasoning, or are they more about hitting political environmental goals even if it hurts the manufacturing sector?",
